	<p>With over a <strong>decade of experience</strong>, I specialize in transforming complex ideas into sleek, high-performing websites and applications. Currently, I'm a <strong>senior frontend developer at Web Africa</strong>, where I lead the development of innovative, user-friendly features, working remotely from the beautiful <strong>Muizenberg</strong>, <strong>South Africa</strong>.</p>

	<p class="flex gap-3 mt-4">
		<a href="https://cal.com/garethlegrange" class="font-mono flex items-center space-x-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm rounded-full py-2 px-4 bg-neutral-900 text-neutral-50">
